<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an [Seitz Marschall von Oberndorf,] Hauptmann von Höchstädt an der Donau</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Ulrich Schwab, Diener der Stadt, wegen der von den Adressaten beschlagnahmten Waren Nürnberger Bürger und Kaufleute an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_236" id="117r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_236_r1l1">Den ~ Hauptleuten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_236_r1l2">cʒu <expan>höhſtete<ex>n</ex></expan> an der Tunaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_236_r1l3">. <expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> . <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vns 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt </del> iſt fürbraht worden . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_236_r1l4">vvie 
<del rend="strikethrough">et </del> Jr <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgern</ex></expan> vnd kauffleuten <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_236_r1l5">etvvieuil hab vnd kauffmanſchaft aufgehalten habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_236_r1l6">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd </del> darümb ſenden vvir cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Swab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_236_r1l7"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener cʒeiger dicʒ briefs mit euch dauon ʒureden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_236_r1l8">vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc vt in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_236" id="117r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den hauptleuten czu <expan>Höhstete<ex>n</ex></expan> an der Tunaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, uns ist fürbraht worden, wie ir
                                <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> und kauffleuten
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> etwievil hab und kauffmanschaft
                        aufgehalten habt, darümb senden wir czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        erberkeit <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Swab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, czeiger dicz briefs, mit euch davon
                        zureden. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                                <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
